n
P_r=\frac{1}{n}+\frac{r-1}{n}\bigg(\frac{1}{r}+\frac{1}{r+1}+\dots+\frac{1}{n-1}\bigg).
P_{r+1}-P_r=\frac{1}{n}\bigg(\frac{1}{r}+\frac{1}{r+1}+\dots+\frac{1}{n-1}-1\bigg).\tag{1}
\bigg(\frac{1}{r}+\frac{1}{r+1}+\dots+\frac{1}{n-1}\bigg)\leq1.\tag2
\bigg(\frac{1}{r^*}+\frac{1}{r^*+1}+\dots+\frac{1}{n-1}\bigg)\approx1.\tag3
